A father pushed his child into the crocodile's mouth. Initially, little Lingyang was stuck in the crocodile's mouth. His father, standing on the shore, was constantly watching him, so he thought that his father would save him when he got the chance. But what happened was something no one had imagined. Little Lingyang kept looking at his father again and again, but Lingyang's father just stood quietly and watched everything. The good thing was that the water there was not very deep, so the crocodile could not show him its deadly twisting move. Then little Lingyang shook himself hard and somehow got out of its grip. As soon as he came out, instead of running away, he turned back and looked into the water again, then his father did something that no one could even imagine - he pushed his own child towards the water again.

snippet.description:
To get a wool sweater, a mischievous kitten secretly shaves a sleeping sheep lady bald and uses the wool to make a new outfit for itself. When the sheep wakes up and finds herself bare, she flies into a rage, chasing the kitten with a wooden stick. She ties the kitten to a chair, shaves its fur, and locks it in a cage. The terrified kitten cries out for help, and a passing black cat, upon seeing this, takes a photo and shows it to the kitten‚Äôs father. Enraged by his child‚Äôs suffering, the cat dad storms the sheep lady‚Äôs house, ties her up, and beats her, finally rescuing the kitten. This intense conflict sparked by wool theft ends with the father and son hugging and crying. What kind of love - hate story lies behind all this? Watch and find out!
